# Anime Vista

Anime Vista is a sleek and powerful anime discovery platform built with modern web technologies. It allows users to explore thousands of anime titles, interact with an anime-savvy AI chatbot, and enjoy a smooth, responsive interface. Powered by both the Jikan API and a custom-built anime API, Anime Vista offers extensive content, user-friendly features, and a stylish UI designed for anime lovers.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔍 Browse and search anime using the [Jikan API](https://jikan.moe/) and a custom-built database of 2000+ titles.
- 🧠 Chat with a Gemini-powered AI bot that knows everything about anime.
- 🔐 Secure authentication via **Auth.js**.
- 💾 MongoDB for user data and favorites.
- ⚡ Fast, modern, and responsive UI built with **Tailwind CSS** and **shadcn/ui**.
- 🚀 Built with **Next.js** for server-side rendering and fast performance.

---

## 🚀 Demo

- **Live Website**: [https://anime-vista-eight.vercel.app/]
- **Anime API**: [https://anime-vista-api-showcase.vercel.app/]

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React, Next.js, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui
- **Authentication**: Auth.js
- **Database**: MongoDB
- **APIs**:
  - Jikan API (MyAnimeList data)
  - Custom REST API (2,000+ anime entries)
- **AI**: Gemini (Google AI)

---

## 📦 Installation

```bash
# Clone the project
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/anime-vista.git
cd anime-vista

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Setup environment variables
cp .env.example .env.local

# Start the development server
npm run dev
